{
    "poem_title": "- CLXXVI - A un sueño ",
    "corpus": "adso",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "author": "Juan de Tassis y Peralta",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "n": "1",
                    "line_text": "¡Aguarda, sombra inquietadora, espera!",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "n": "2",
                    "line_text": "Si de causa cruel naces cobarde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--++--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "n": "3",
                    "line_text": "cuando mi queja tu rigor aguarde",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "n": "4",
                    "line_text": "será tu asombro la merced postrera.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "¡Aguarda, sombra inquietadora, espera!\nSi de causa cruel naces cobarde,\ncuando mi queja tu rigor aguarde\nserá tu asombro la merced postrera."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "n": "5",
                    "line_text": "Apareces piadosa y huyes fiera,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "n": "6",
                    "line_text": "de tus efectos conocido alarde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "n": "7",
                    "line_text": "que aún sombra falta que del mal me guarde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "n": "8",
                    "line_text": "o bien fingido, porque amando muera.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Apareces piadosa y huyes fiera,\nde tus efectos conocido alarde,\nque aún sombra falta que del mal me guarde,\no bien fingido, porque amando muera."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "n": "9",
                    "line_text": "Lisonjero traidor, tirano dueño,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "n": "10",
                    "line_text": "su gusto obliga, su inclemencia asombra,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "n": "11",
                    "line_text": "a leve prueba, cauteloso engaña.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Lisonjero traidor, tirano dueño,\nsu gusto obliga, su inclemencia asombra,\na leve prueba, cauteloso engaña."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "n": "12",
                    "line_text": "¡Sueño enemigo, si mis glorias sueño,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "n": "13",
                    "line_text": "con la luz que me animas me acompaña,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "n": "14",
                    "line_text": "que en mis tormentos el alivio es sombra!",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+---+++-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "¡Sueño enemigo, si mis glorias sueño,\ncon la luz que me animas me acompaña,\nque en mis tormentos el alivio es sombra!"
        }
    ]
}